{"tid":1909812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"亞馬遜將大批「天價」防疫貨物下架","createTime":"2020-03-04T08:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T09:45:07.000Z","uid":25468,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5a2a2dac6f57281cad222d677e490487636050aa","tid":1909812,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.smalltechnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/frc-b129f5251975a9aef010dd5b825f2797.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smalltechnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2Ffrc-b129f5251975a9aef010dd5b825f2797.png&h=c10add19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒疫情持續，不少人透過上網購買口罩等保護裝備，購物網站不時有賣家定出天文數字售價。網上零售巨頭亞馬遜表示，近日已經將數以萬計以「天價」開售的物件下架。<br />\n<br />\n同時下架的，還有聲稱可以對付新型冠狀病毒的貨品，亞馬遜說涉及的貨品數目超過100萬件。<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司報道，亞馬遜發言人指公司不容許炒賣行為，對於在全球陷入衞生危機時，有賣家提高基本衞生物品的售價，亞馬遜對此深感失望，因此根據公司指引將數以萬計貨品下架。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜又指，公司一直要求賣家提供正確產品資料，因此已經將違反規定的貨品下架，重申會在打擊假貨上與當局及執法部門合作。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜不是首個阻止賣家藉疫情圖利的平台，社交網站Facebook在上月底宣布，禁止宣稱可以預防感染或治愈新型冠狀病毒的產品在Facebook賣廣告。<br />\n<br />\n針對這個情況，一批跨黨派美國國會議員計劃提出法案，提出如果電子購物平台賣假貨，將要負上法律責任，以加強消費者權益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=382976&amp;fbclid=IwAR1sAQ2rtyENxGIF92bWhbQ_FdDolPl4V3xbFTsIKETwELd6InS0cKWJXw0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D382976%26fbclid%3DIwAR1sAQ2rtyENxGIF92bWhbQ_FdDolPl4V3xbFTsIKETwELd6InS0cKWJXw0&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=ec7602b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D382976%26fbclid%3DIwAR1sAQ2rtyENxGIF92bWhbQ_FdDolPl4V3xbFTsIKETwELd6InS0cKWJXw0&h=08726b23\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=382976&amp;fbclid=IwAR1sAQ2rtyENxGIF92bWhbQ_FdDolPl4V3xbFTsIKETwELd6InS0cKWJXw0</a>"},{"pid":"78e7430511f008265601aa88a8af01d84a4d441d","tid":1909812,"uid":17859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"同共賊相映成趣"},{"pid":"b25645f47d807353a9849dae6a0a4365183488a6","tid":1909812,"uid":9594,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:34:52.000Z","msg":"應該拉晒班人去打靶就啱"},{"pid":"e29afeebbcfaafaf8c1cf842f7f9c99b8f28fde9","tid":1909812,"uid":246118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:36:01.000Z","msg":"美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反觀香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，周圍都炒緊，仲要炒必需品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb1ee1fafffd291bad1ea13de01193a761d7f9c","tid":1909812,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:44:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9299ba3252a9cddb930ff7ea8737ff56e9628b70","tid":1909812,"uid":79919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"正皮"},{"pid":"8b61dc23fde8d09b506dca7659f27913e77b1a21","tid":1909812,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e29afeebbcfaafaf8c1cf842f7f9c99b8f28fde9","tid":1909812,"uid":246118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:36:01.000Z","msg":"美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反觀香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，周圍都炒緊，仲要炒必需品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:50:35.000Z","msg":"香港代表<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bOfdYjF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbOfdYjF.jpg&h=e62cfa42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30f0fc5024ea5f8550c3860d44394d9b053bb596","tid":1909812,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2fb1ee1fafffd291bad1ea13de01193a761d7f9c","tid":1909812,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1